fragment.aboutText: Rich Boy Mafia Independent Record Label equips professional artists with every element needed to thrive in the music industry. We have the most accomplished audio engineers, photographers and videographers in Austin.
fragment.artistText: Born and Raised in The Live Music Capitol of the World ; Austin, Texas Scotty Jamz is one of the most multifaceted artists in hiphop. Labeled as the “Hardest Mexican rapper” in the game , his music unites the essences of Gangsta rap to his hispanic roots. His father bought him his first ever mic and begged him to make good use of his talents which he heard loud and clear. Starting his craft in the garage with a beat up computer and passion to be the best, has brought Scotty to produce some of the most infectious hooks & storytelling rap that parallels no one else.   SXSW showcase appearances, touring the nation and an appearance at the Alaska Hiphop awards have groomed Scotty to take the world by storm in 2021.
fragment.musicText: Sean Gordon a.k.a 10kgohard_ commands the studio, with melodies that take your ears on a journey making you forget the destination.  Born in Austin, Texas to Jamaican parents, while also spending time in Europe playing professional soccer has stretched his range, allowing him to produce beats for any type of artist. Sean’s most recent beat featured on a track that hit 25k views in its first week.
